As already observed by [petroni-etal-2019-language], prompt formulations influence LLM responses, and hence the resulting KB. \ourkb\ presents one way of materializing LLM knowledge into structured format, but better prompts may exist. In line with [petroni-etal-2019-language], methods like ours therefore always inform about lower bounds (on LLM factual knowledge, in our case).